data.description: Welcome to your cozy modern rancher in District 49! This updated home features a stylish kitchen, laminate flooring, and an open layout filled with natural light. Enjoy stainless steel appliances, updated lighting, and a bright Owner's Suite with a private bath and walk-in closet. Relish Colorado's sunshine through large windows and relax in the fully fenced backyard with a spacious patio and beautiful mature trees.
